HEADWORD: Skittles
<hw>Skit"tles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[Of Scand.
origin. ⟦root⟧159. See <er>Shoot</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>, and cf.
<er>Shuttle</er>, <er>Skit</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <def>An English
game resembling ninepins, but played by throwing wooden disks, instead
of rolling balls, at the pins.</def>⟦br⟧
